Given the following program and the variable in complex data type, decompose the it into variables with primary data type.. The program is 
int fn2(int p1, int p2) { return p1 - p2; }

int t;
int v_int;
short w;
unsigned ac = 1;

int main() {
  short an;
  w = 0;
  an = 0x294A;
  int ac_val = ac;
  short w_val = w;
  short an_val = an;
  t = ac_val || (an_val = w_val);
  short ao = 0xBCD1;
  int temp = ao - (1 - an_val);
  v_int = fn2(temp, t) & 1;
  printf("checksum = %d\n", v_int);
  return 0;
}
.                 The target to be optimized is temp: It is an int variable, and its value is calculated as ao - (1 - an)..
